{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "strings": {
    "Download & Load": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Laden & Aktivieren"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "読み込み & 有効化"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cancel": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Abbrechen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キャンセル"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Delete cached model": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zwischengespeichertes Modell löschen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キャッシュされたモデルを削除"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Download timed out while fetching Gemma 4 from Hugging Face. Please retry. Adding an optional HuggingFace token in this plugin can also increase download rate limits.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Download von Gemma 4 von Hugging Face hat zu lange gedauert. Bitte erneut versuchen. Ein optionaler HuggingFace-Token in diesem Plugin kann die Download-Rate-Limits erhoehen."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hugging FaceからGemma 4のダウンロードが長すぎました。再度試してください。このプラグインでオプションのHuggingFaceトークンを使用すると、ダウンロードレート制限を高めることができます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Downloading or preparing %@ has not made progress for several minutes. Cancel, delete the cached model if one is shown, and try again. Adding an optional HuggingFace token may also help if Hugging Face is throttling downloads.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Beim Laden oder Vorbereiten von %@ gab es mehrere Minuten keinen Fortschritt. Breche ab, lösche das zwischengespeicherte Modell, falls es angezeigt wird, und versuche es erneut. Ein optionaler HuggingFace-Token kann ebenfalls helfen, wenn Hugging Face Downloads drosselt."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ のダウンロードまたは準備が数分間進んでいません。キャンセルし、表示されている場合はキャッシュされたモデルを削除してから再試行してください。Hugging Face のダウンロードが制限されている場合は、オプションの HuggingFace トークンも役立つことがあります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The downloaded Gemma model cache appears incomplete or incompatible. Delete the cached model and download it again.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der heruntergeladene Gemma-Modellcache scheint unvollständig oder inkompatibel zu sein. Lösche das zwischengespeicherte Modell und lade es erneut herunter."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ダウンロードされたGemmaモデルキャッシュは不完全または互換性がないようです。キャッシュされたモデルを削除し、再度ダウンロードしてください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "HuggingFace Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HuggingFace Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HuggingFace トークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Load a Gemma 4 model in Integrations before using it for prompts.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lade zuerst ein Gemma-4-Modell in den Integrationen, bevor du es fuer Prompts verwendest."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "プロンプトでGemma 4モデルを使用する前に、統合からGemma 4モデルをまず読み込みます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Local LLM powered by Google Gemma 4 on Apple Silicon. No API key required.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lokales LLM mit Google Gemma 4 auf Apple Silicon. Kein API-Schlüssel erforderlich."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple Silicon上でGoogle Gemma 4を使用したローカルLLM。APIキー不要。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Model": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Modell"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モデル"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Invalid HuggingFace Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ungültiger HuggingFace-Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無効なHuggingFaceトークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Experimental": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Experimentell"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "実験的"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Experimental. You can try it at your own risk.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Experimentell. Du kannst es auf eigene Gefahr ausprobieren."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "実験的です。ご自身の責任で試してみてください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Valid HuggingFace Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gültiger HuggingFace-Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有効なHuggingFaceトークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Validating token...": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Token wird geprüft..."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "トークンの検証中..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optional. Increases download rate limits. Free at huggingface.co/settings/tokens": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Optional. Erhoeht Download-Rate-Limits. Kostenlos unter huggingface.co/settings/tokens"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "オプション。ダウンロードレート制限を高めます。huggingface.co/settings/tokensで無料で取得可能です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Remove": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Entfernen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "削除"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Save": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Speichern"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保存"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Gemma 4 E2B/E4B 4-bit models are recommended. Larger variants are experimental and may fail depending on hardware.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gemma 4 E2B/E4B 4-bit Modelle sind empfohlen. Groessere Varianten sind experimentell und koennen je nach Hardware fehlschlagen."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gemma 4 E2B/E4B 4-bitモデルが推奨されます。より大きいバリアントは実験的であり、ハードウェアによっては失敗する可能性があります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Try anyway": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Trotzdem versuchen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "それでも試す"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unload": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deaktivieren"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無効化"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version": "1.0"
}
